snippet.title: Kick Ass Commandos Trailer
snippet.description:
Lock and Load! It's time to KickAss and... Well, it's just time to KickAss. Grab your machinegun, flamethrower, rocket launcher and grenades. 

Get it on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/359140

Assault the enemy base and free commandos to join your team while you destroy everything you see. Make your way through enemy bunkers to rescue your comrades, and kill everyone else you encounter.
